---
title: Sweet Potato & Quinoa Salad with Avocado, Orange, and Arugula
description: This salad is full of nutrient-dense ingredients like sweet potatoes, quinoa, avocado, and orange. It’s proof that healthy doesn’t have to mean boring! Almonds and feta finish the dish with crunch and tang.
